This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically investigating a state-of-the-art paragraph embedding method and proposing a new objective to improve its performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions downstream classification tasks, which could relate to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
